Paxton travels to Maxwell for showdown Posted: Wednesday, October 7, 2015 4:19 pm Paxton travels to Maxwell for showdown By Andrew Bottrell abottrell@nptelegraph.com nptelegraph.com 
Two area teams hope to keep their playoff dreams alive on Friday night when Paxton travels to Maxwell for this week’s Telegraph Game of the Week. 
The Tigers (1-4 overall, 0-2 in D2-9 District) come into the game off a tough, one-point loss to Brady in the district opener, the second close loss the Tigers have suffered this season.     Subscription required
